@node Bugs  "ClipWizard V1.1 - Bugs"
The match search is only done to the first 255 characters in the
clipboard. The GetClipContents arexx-command is still giving the
whole contents. I hope I can manage to fix this soon.

If you find any bugs, please contact me. See @{"Author" LINK Author} for
details.
@endnode
